{"tid":1383351,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[真心想問] 其實係現場影相有咩問題？","createTime":"2019-07-29T16:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T18:28:11.000Z","uid":229254,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1bfb3bee86b01b4f0508f8e68f9f224b9e250b8c","tid":1383351,"uid":229254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:21:34.000Z","msg":"理性討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家成日屌人唔比影相<br />\n影大頭有問題呢個大家都明<br />\n咁影wide shot見唔到樣又有咩問題呢？"},{"pid":"ddb159890fc830230371fa880f5f01e5fc4dad55","tid":1383351,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:22:30.000Z","msg":"冇人知你影緊乜"},{"pid":"507b4d524e018a97088c7b6829082bda1ce527bd","tid":1383351,"uid":235580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:22:34.000Z","msg":"全部手足同我推！ 如何令黑警有所顧忌有所恐懼！ 如何從狗屋內部分解黑警！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378251</a>"},{"pid":"f5f825337f3433a814c45d9ff7f280d0cc2e4344","tid":1383351,"uid":237175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:24:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a29a3d4ba92ddd3d2f0fef133eb018f869b20916","tid":1383351,"uid":273794,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:25:40.000Z","msg":"咁得閒影相幫下手好過啦"},{"pid":"a08939c94d2e653a482e7d1bf6ce343b0bf2df62","tid":1383351,"uid":199799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:26:39.000Z","msg":"冇人知你影乜 廢事引起誤會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要影證據既有記者朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c5008a2f0d2a2af3eb965947b5c5b8823c05f5","tid":1383351,"uid":229254,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T17:00:39.000Z","msg":"係而家呢個年代基本上係全民皆記者，每個人都有自己渠道去將發生緊嘅野記錄同傳開去。現場所見有好多上左年紀嘅人會影相（唔係嚟挑機影大頭個d），可能係好奇，可能想影低送去朋友圈都未定，咁樣都算係一種exposure。唔洗下下見到人都話唔撚比影相，有d真係見住佢部電話佢影wide shot都比一句屌埋嚟。<br />\n<br />\n相反而家愈嚟愈多記者，你估著住反光衣寫著press就信得過？港人港地、幫港出聲、HK G報呢d 19媒體都係註冊新聞機構，佢地都有記者證做採訪，比佢地影到仲恐怖啦屌。"},{"pid":"341a6593444efe6a70ec8e74a52786fd068d813d","tid":1383351,"uid":21961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:15:56.000Z","msg":"好睇你影緊咩<br />\n拆鐵馬你又影<br />\n起磚你又影<br />\n係中間位置除口罩休息你又影<br />\n咁咪比人嘈兩句<br />\n<br />\n老老實實除咗同狗搏鬥緊<br />\n好似咬手指個單咁<br />\n你由制服個下影冇人會屌你<br />\n仲可以見住插眼先咬手指添<br />\n唔係嘅話你影嘅每張相都係告入義士嘅證據"},{"pid":"3d7cfa30ccb138024f282b1d1055949c97805cd7","tid":1383351,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T18:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得阻唔到咁多影相嘅人 個個都有手機<br />\n記者又有大炮又有live<br />\n個個都著到Alan walker咁 點影都唔驚"}]}